#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:7
msgctxt "Mood.label"
msgid "mood"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:8
msgctxt "Mood.description"
msgid ""
"Mood represents how happy or stressed someone is. If mood gets too low, the "
"person may suffer a mental break. Depending on how low their mood is, "
"someone who has a mental break may have a minor breaks like hiding in their "
"room for a day, or a major break like going on a murder spree."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:24
msgctxt "Food.label"
msgid "food"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:25
msgctxt "Food.description"
msgid ""
"Food is the amount of nutrition a creature has consumed recently. If it is "
"at zero, a creature will become increasingly malnourished and eventually "
"die."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:36
msgctxt "Rest.label"
msgid "sleep"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:37
msgctxt "Rest.description"
msgid ""
"Sleep is how much time a creature has spent sleeping recently. If it is at "
"zero, a creature will eventually fall asleep on the spot."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:47
msgctxt "Joy.label"
msgid "recreation"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:48
msgctxt "Joy.description"
msgid ""
"Recreation is the need to have fun. Repeating the same kind of activity "
"makes it less fun, so variety is necessary."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:63
msgctxt "Beauty.label"
msgid "beauty"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:64
msgctxt "Beauty.description"
msgid ""
"Beauty reflects how visually pleasing a person has found their surroundings "
"recently. Beautiful things like art improve beauty when viewed, while ugly "
"things like filth and rough stone surfaces reduce it."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:77
msgctxt "Comfort.label"
msgid "comfort"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:78
msgctxt "Comfort.description"
msgid ""
"Comfort is gained by sitting in or sleeping on comfortable furniture. It is "
"acquired while laying in bed, sitting in a chair while working, or other "
"times."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:92
msgctxt "Outdoors.label"
msgid "outdoors"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:93
msgctxt "Outdoors.description"
msgid ""
"Outdoors expresses the need not to be cooped up inside. It is harmed by long"
" periods inside, especially underground. It improves when someone spends "
"time under the sky, especially outdoors. It's not about the size of the "
"rooms, but the need to be outside from time to time. Lack of outdoors time "
"is a significant challenge for people who dwell in underground bases."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:103
msgctxt "Indoors.label"
msgid "indoors"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:104
msgctxt "Indoors.description"
msgid ""
"Indoors expresses the need to be within walls and under a roof. It is harmed"
" by spending time in outdoor areas or not under roofs. To raise this need "
"past 50%, a person must be under an overhead mountain, not just a normal "
"roof."
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:114
msgctxt "DrugDesire.label"
msgid "chemical"
msgstr ""

#: Defs/NeedDefs/Needs.xml:115
msgctxt "DrugDesire.description"
msgid ""
"Chemical expresses the desire to ingest drugs. When above a certain level it"
" will create good mood, but when below a certain level it will create "
"increasingly bad mood."
msgstr ""

